reviewText: My daughter saw the previews for this "new DVD" on one of our other Barbie movies, and of course, had to have it. So, I got it for her 5th birthday this summer. We have only watched it a few times since then.This was definatly misleading in the advertisements...making it seem like they were songs from the movies we love shown with new barbie clips or videos of the songs, Not true.  We own all the movies featured on the DVD, so really this was pointless.  It simply shows clips (even the talking parts which I find very annoying and odd when you are trying to sing along) of the movie that the song was taken from. No new footage, or videos or anything you would expect from a new DVD.The lights that light up the words to follow along is WAY off; so if my child really could read, she wouldn't be able to follow along b/c it seems to only highlight several words at a time, unlike a real sing along.What was most annoying was the fact they kept bits and pieces from movies in there cutting off half of the songs...really? You couldn't have used another soundtrack for those parts? But my daughters love it and when she had her little 4 yr old cousin over this summer, she seemed to love it too.If given the choice, I wouldn't recommend it unless you do not already own the other Barbie movies which the songs are coming from.  Otherwise, just watch the movies you already have and you pretty much have seen this one.
summary: Not a NEW Movie; Just clips from old movies
